      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Your perfect musical cues can accentuate a moment of triumph and send a surge of adrenaline through an ally.</p><p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.feats.PFb03QqUCjFrTTDo]{Crescendo of Violence}</p><hr><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When an ally within 30 feet of you scores a critical hit against a significant foe, as a reaction you can spend 1 Resolve Point and a charge of a sonic weapon you’re holding. The ally regains Stamina Points equal to 3 × your level or 4 × the number of @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.GMkLZsN3a7YPvA03.JournalEntryPage.bD4kmdFU7wwsenOf]{Profession} (musician) ranks you have, whichever is higher.</p><p><br><em>If Profession musician is not your first profession, edit formula in Details tab to reference the correct skill.</em></p>"
